{"tid":1569711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用長者八達通，党铁唔會賺少左！","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T19:04:54.000Z","uid":321134,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a98f4f3419fb3bf9030178fcd8ca38a574266c4","tid":1569711,"uid":321134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"公共交通票價優惠計劃 (不論長者兩蚊/學生)，都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span></strong></span>地鐵公司自己提供嘅優惠，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[b<span style=\"color: red;\">]係政府提供</span>[/b]</span>！<br />\n<br />\n例如：坐党铁由荃灣去銅鑼灣<br />\n成人價：党铁收$15.2 <br />\n長者價：$2 + $13.2 (公帑比) = 党铁收$15.2 <br />\n<br />\n姐係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>用長者八達通唔會令党铁賺少咗</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日多左 <span style=\"color: pink;\">food panda</span> 跳閘風險上升，加上個人不主張跳閘。所以鼓勵大家可以用以下方式<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抵制党铁</span></span></strong>：<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔Q搭！<strong>改變自己搭車習慣</strong>！<br />\n2. 唔幫襯党铁商場！<br />\n3. 學689梁副主席數廣告，邊個喺党铁落廣告就恥與為伍！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">扺制黨鐵，恥與為伍</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b8db55ce9e27788c39b93cce917b222267d86cf4","tid":1569711,"uid":145923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"黨鐵賺既唔係車費，係地產項目。"},{"pid":"087deffb25717ef26f4817a122a0ae809a101387","tid":1569711,"uid":108337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"但你慳左錢可以做多更多野"},{"pid":"92ebdad03e13a1198f5a064261684a7e1ec282ab","tid":1569711,"uid":13642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b078a3deb93ba89bf051a82b8c6c2d2505efef0","tid":1569711,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"仲有港鐵旗下的私人屋苑都係收入來源"},{"pid":"ca843d9fe7e2ff74dced58bb028e24776b7f8bcd","tid":1569711,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:51:06.000Z","msg":"政府比錢 咪姐係我地賺返政府錢囉"},{"pid":"be2736c9a2346c3b4c85f3d156dd651ff3ca2259","tid":1569711,"uid":105526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:22:33.000Z","msg":"黨鐵就係政府既一部分，佢點樣都唔會蝕，既然係咁，不如我地節省開支"},{"pid":"3900029a4e827d9ae01021019e7d2634ebfa4cb0","tid":1569711,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:04:54.000Z","msg":"罷坐啦 一蚊都唔好益佢"}]}